title: Hugo Advanced French
description:
Hugo Advanced French
Published 2004.

Three CDs, narrated by native speakers, guide you through the carefully structured, week-by-week course.  

Learn how to improve your French speaking, writing, reading and listening skills. Basic grammar is revised and new structures are clearly explained whilst exercises based on real-life scenarios reinforce your understanding of the latest slang, idiom and more advanced grammatical structures.

Complete mp3 and pdf files.
